<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Seat Booking Success</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f2f2f2;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #333;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #666;
      }

      ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
      }

      li {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #666;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #0062cc;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Seat Booking Success</h1>
      <p>Your seat has been successfully booked.</p>
      <p>Here are the details of your booking:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Seat Number: [Redirect Number]</li>
        <li>Date: [Redirect Date]</li>
        <li>Time: [Redirect Time]/li></li>
      </ul>

      <p>Thank you for using our library.</p>
      <a href="/" class="btn">Book Another Seat</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
